'''蘭斯·克勞瑟'''（{{lang-en|'''Lance Crouther'''}}，{{bd|1962年|5月31日}}）是一位[[美國|美國]]男編劇、製片人和演員。較知名的是在電影《{{le|來去天堂|Down to Earth (2001 film)}}》（2001年）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/bostonherald/access/68721515.html?dids=68721515:68721515&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Feb+16%2C+2001&author=James+Verniere&pub=Boston+Herald&desc=MOVIE+REVIEW%3B+Heaven+Can+Rock%3B+Here+comes+TV's+funniest+comic+in+delighful+remake |title=MOVIE REVIEW; Heaven Can Rock; Here comes TV's funniest comic in delighful remake |publisher=Pqasb.pqarchiver.com |date=2001-02-16 |accessdate=2012-06-13}}</ref>、《{{le|好頭髮|Good Hair}}》（2009年）<ref>[http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CSTB&p_theme=cstb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=12B3D0AEC1B729C8&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D ''Good Hair''] {{Wayback|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CSTB&p_theme=cstb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=12B3D0AEC1B729C8&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D |date=20180228162004 }}, ''Chicago Sun Times''</ref>、電視劇《{{le|Wanda at Large}}》（2003年）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/318250201.html?dids=318250201:318250201&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Mar+26%2C+2003&author=Allan+Johnson%2C+Tribune+television+reporter&pub=Chicago+Tribune&desc=Writer%2C+producer%2C+performer+--+a+comedian+called+Wanda |title=Writer, producer, performer - a comedian called Wanda |publisher=Pqasb.pqarchiver.com |date=2003-03-26 |accessdate=2012-06-13 |first=Allan |last=Johnson |archive-date=2012-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107223736/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/318250201.html?dids=318250201:318250201&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Mar+26,+2003&author=Allan+Johnson,+Tribune+television+reporter&pub=Chicago+Tribune&desc=Writer,+producer,+performer+--+a+comedian+called+Wanda |dead-url=no }}</ref>和深夜節目《{{le|洛佩茲之夜|Lopez Tonight}}》（2009年至2010年）中擔任編劇。而克勞瑟也於[[路易·C·K|路易·C·K]]執導的2001年電影《[[嘻哈奇俠|嘻哈奇俠]]》中主演菩提·譚<ref>{{cite news |last=Bonin |first=Liane |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,165795,00.html |title=Stop Making Sense |publisher=EW.com |date=2001-07-02 |accessdate=2012-06-13 |archive-date=2013-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211092242/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,165795,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

克勞瑟已提名了四項[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]，並贏得了一座{{link-en|黃金時段艾美獎綜藝節目最佳編劇|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Writing for a Variety Series}}。他較常與[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]合作。

